{
  "texts": [
    "Based on all these considerations, we chose the Chinese Translators Journal and Target: International Journal of Translation Studies as the target journals.",
    "Articles in the former are published in Chinese with an English translation of each abstract, while articles in the latter are published all in English.",
    "When selecting translated abstracts, we singled out the translations reformulated from Chinese source texts because there were no equivalences between translations and their source texts.",
    "When collecting English original abstracts, we determined whether the authors were English native speakers based on their affiliations and personal profiles.",
    "Moreover, too short texts were excluded since it is difficult to observe linguistic regularities in such texts."
  ]
}